full_title: Night Tube by Saiming (Ft. Zuko Rosemeid)
title: Night Tube
lyrics:
3 ContributorsNight Tube Lyrics[Verse 1: Zuko Rosemeid]

Like, yes indeed

Lock into we for the best in scеne

[Verse 3: Zuko Rosemeid]
Chit chat on the Snapchat, don't move mad cause she's got a fat back
Make sure you pattern your reason, pattern your why and pattern your stack
Heard your track last week on Capital FM bro I only heard cap
Go back to bars, pree them lyrics, take out the lies and go fix that

[Verse 4: Saiming]
S.M.S-travagant man
Been rappin' since 10, wait 15
Now I'm slicin' them by pen s.a.i.m.i.n.g
